original_title: UFC Fight Night 152: Dos Anjos vs. Lee
overview: UFC Fight Night 152: Dos Anjos vs. Lee was a mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship that was held on May 18, 2019 at Blue Cross Arena in Rochester, New York. A welterweight bout between former UFC Lightweight Champion Rafael dos Anjos and former interim lightweight title challenger Kevin Lee served as the event headliner.
title: UFC Fight Night 152: Dos Anjos vs. Lee
